content.rendered:
BOSS AIR TRIPLE AIRBAG 2603 COMPLETE

Boss Air Triple Airbag 2603 Complete available for order now through Automax 4×4! Order online, come in & see us or give us a call on (02) 6699 2744 for a quote!

The #2603 triple bag complete have the same diameter as the #2600 bag but with 1 extra bellow making for a genuine 10″ travel (Extended height approx 380MM) airbag, perfect for coil replacements in 4wd vehicles and off road situations.

Includes:

  • 2600lb Extreme Series Triple Bag
  • Top and Bottom plate and stainless bolts.
  • 12 countersunk stainless bolts

Specs:

  • Fully compressed – 75mm with 6mm ends fitted
  • Max diameter – 190mm (widest when fully compressed)
  • Max Height – 380mm
  • Max working pressure 0-160psi
  • Test pressure – 480psi
  • Burst pressure – 1000psi
To view the range of Boss Air products available, CLICK HERE!
Follow us on Instagram and Facebook to keep up to date with what’s going on in our workshop!
